<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-debt">in debt</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>欠 (某人) 债；受 (某人) 恩惠：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nearly half the college students said they were in debt.
近一半的大学生说自己欠债。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m in debt to him for his help. 
对于他的帮助，我欠他一份人情。</p></div></div>